Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.68,0:00:18.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think I used my head too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:21.04,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My shoulders are sore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.88,0:00:23.70,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They feel so heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:39.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From the silent depths
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:46.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The pillars awaken from ages-long sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:53.65,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Crimson blood
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:01:00.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Summons the valorous to stand up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:08.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If inherited love is called fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.83,0:01:15.01,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then take another step with smiling eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:21.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mystify the darkness, dodge in a blink
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:25.27,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Avoid the blade,\Nfind an opening and strike
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:31.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Conviction tested\Nopens the way to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:36.03,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Like a bloody storm\NHot like a bloody stone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:39.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny written into your veins
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:45.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The undying bonds of honor arise
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:50.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take hold of them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:59.64,Type,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter 18: Von Stroheim's Revenge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:01:59.64,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:05.85,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar and JoJo should be back\Nbefore too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:07.81,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Lisa Lisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:10.81,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which blouse do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:13.07,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Suzie Q, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:18.53,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,White is always nice,\Nbut something colorful can be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:20.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:23.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:25.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How about the white one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:29.04,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I really do like this design.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:33.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did JoJo and Caesar\Npass their final exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:35.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:37.42,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:41.34,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go with\Nthe refreshing white!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:42.85,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Suzie Q...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:43.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:47.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Send Caesar and JoJo to my room\Nwhen they arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:49.14,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.59,0:02:54.61,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I really like the clean design\Nof this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:56.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which is better?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:58.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which to choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:02:59.49,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,White!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.75,0:03:00.99,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:02.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is nice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:05.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:08.84,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The colorful one\Nwill do nicely, Suzie Q.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:10.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good choice, madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:25.89,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just leave these here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:30.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clean up the broken glass later.\NBe careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:31.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:54.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Suzie Q.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:01.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you screaming about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:02.84,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet, dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:05.64,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who... Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.64,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's a stranger on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.85,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're calling me a stranger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:14.35,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! Joseph Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:17.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:19.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:22.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You always had a mask on before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:24.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:27.95,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't seen my face\Nin all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:31.83,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And so? Am I handsome?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.29,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Weird lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:41.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even with these weird lips,\Nif we were to fall in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:46.19,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...you can kiss them all you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:48.64,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In your dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Blech!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:55.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:57.71,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:04:58.77,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:03.65,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Madam Lisa Lisa wants you\Nto go to her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:07.53,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But she's in the bath,\Nso wait half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:10.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. I planned to go anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:13.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They know about the Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:17.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Madam Lisa Lisa's Stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:21.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.\NYou don't want to get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:26.38,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Um, JoJo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:27.72,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:32.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're actually pretty hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:41.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:44.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My shoulders have loosened up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:55.20,Type,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One ring neutralized at 6 a.m.\NThe other dissolves in six days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:06:00.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The news I have is important,\Nbut Lisa Lisa is taking a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:03.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm supposed to wait half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:17.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I was told to wait, I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.19,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where to spend half an hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:23.99,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think the best place is here\Nby Lisa Lisa's door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:29.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be wrong if I peeked\Nthrough the keyhole?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.70,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.04,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Suzie Q?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:44.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's she doing in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:47.30,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When did she go inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:48.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:51.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she was on the docks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:55.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:58.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The knob is covered in slime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:08.69,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, Suzie Q, have JoJo and Caesar\Nreturned yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:13.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Suzie Q?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:28.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Suzie Q!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:31.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you put the Red Stone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:44.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?! Where is the Stone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:46.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:50.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,S-Something's inside Suzie Q!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:59.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You have reduced me to nothing\Nbut a brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:04.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I challenge you to one last fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:08.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I put the Stone on the boat\Nthat just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:12.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am here to stop you from chasing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:15.80,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You will not follow that postal boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:20.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The woman I am inside of\Nis still mostly alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:25.85,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You will have to kill her\Nin order to destroy me completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:30.11,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do that?\NAre you capable of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:32.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Esidisi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:34.11,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:37.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You never give up, do you, Esidisi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:38.99,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:41.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:43.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:45.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:52.52,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You survived your bout with Esidisi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:54.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're a lucky one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:59.64,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo! What were you doing\Nwith our coach?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:01.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cool it, meathead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:04.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that. Look at Suzie Q!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:05.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.28,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:11.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's Esidisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:16.24,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His brain and blood vessels\Nhave taken over her body!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:17.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Save me, Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.65,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:25.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone picks on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:28.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...but you won't, will you, Caesar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:32.70,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fall for it.\NShe's not the one talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:34.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Esidisi is using her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:39.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar, the Stone is on a postal boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:43.85,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to us. Go after the Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:47.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If the Stone reaches a train in Venice
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:52.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we have no idea where\Nin the world it might go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:00.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:05.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You have to kill me first, wiener heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:08.49,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A male voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:12.84,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His blood vessels are controlling her\Nfrom within!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:16.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:18.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:20.69,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Use your Hamon and kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:24.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It would be easy to destroy me\Nin my current state!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:31.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But you know that this girl's heart\Ncan't take a Hamon shock like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:36.11,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you willing to take\Nthis girl's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:41.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you can, then hurry up and do it,\Nfools!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:44.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not soft, Esidisi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:50.62,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I only have to end the life of one girl
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:54.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and I can save the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:58.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I consider it a necessary sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:01.61,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you serious, JoJo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:08.52,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Time to go to pieces, Esidisi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:09.49,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:10.27,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:15.73,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:19.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I can't hit her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:21.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:24.99,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he'd pop out of her,\Nbut he's unfazed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:30.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of your bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:33.73,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You could never kill this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:48.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Stone has likely already\Narrived on the main island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:50.81,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:53.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A-And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:57.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is he doing to Suzie Q now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:59.69,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop this, Esidisi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:04.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And now I will explode this girl's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:09.29,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and cover you all\Nwith blood as hot as lava!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:12.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-His blood is boiling hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:16.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,S-Suzie Q's body is falling apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:21.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If this keeps up, it's not just Suzie Q,\Nwe'll all be in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,V-Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:27.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo, use your Hamon on Suzie Q!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.14,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:32.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:37.69,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I still have nightmares about\Nchopping von Stroheim's leg off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:39.07,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We need a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:45.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll do it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:49.24,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, Coach! Let me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:52.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! I thought of something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:54.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Remember Hell Climb Pillar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:57.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We'll try that! It's do or die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:12:59.04,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:03.17,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You and me! Two types of Hamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:04.54,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Two types?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:07.14,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:10.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-It might just work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:11.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:16.35,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo! Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:18.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:20.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo, follow my breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:23.49,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:37.42,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo creates a burst of positive Hamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:41.80,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar focuses negative Hamon\Non Suzie Q's heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:46.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At that point, the Hamon is\Nnegative positive zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:58.35,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've forced him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:02.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:05.49,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:08.95,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let the sun take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:13.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That low-down scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:17.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hiding away in a girl's body like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:19.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, Caesar. You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:26.07,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I fought with him, so I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:29.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He threw away his pride and did all he
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:32.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\Ncould to get the Stone for his allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:38.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For thousands of years\Nhe lived his life to its fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:40.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it was good or evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:43.69,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I respect his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:48.99,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:14:59.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Suzie Q...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:06.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,While Esidisi controlled you,\Nyou must have been semiconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:07.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Answer this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:10.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the Stone headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:14.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Switzerland.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:17.10,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Saint Moritz.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:18.73,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A package.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:23.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,An envelope with\NMadam Lisa Lisa's crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The address is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:28.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Switzerland?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:31.28,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are Kars and Wamuu there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:33.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I just checked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:37.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A cargo train for Switzerland \Nleft ten minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:40.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Stone has to be on that train!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:47.50,Type,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Saint Moritz\N Venice
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:47.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And we have to beat that train\Nto Saint Moritz!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:52.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In order to keep the Stone\Nout of the wrong hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:55.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we might have to do some dirty work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:00.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We might break the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.77,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Some of us may end up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:05.69,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:09.81,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't ready before,\Nbut I won't lose now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.81,0:16:11.61,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eradicate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:14.62,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:17.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right. We're out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:37.64,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Suzie Q! Look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:41.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is goodbye, Suzie Q!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:45.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll be back in Venice one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:47.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:48.90,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:52.19,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Heal those ugly wounds before then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:58.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:04.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo, you just make sure\Nyou come back here in one piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.08,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be pushy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:09.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You may be an old lady first,\Nbut I'll return!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:14.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:27.65,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:34.70,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Saint Moritz, Switzerland
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Drive the damned car!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:20.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's with your arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:25.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong with the wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:33.34,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Esidisi hasn't called.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:37.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He said he learned\Nthe Stone was in Venice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:40.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Has something happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:44.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, JoJo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:45.60,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:48.64,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:53.36,Type,Default,0000,0000,0000,,5:00 p.m.\N6 days until remaining ring dissolves
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:53.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo, we've caught up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:56.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're in customs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.39,0:19:02.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's less than an hour from \Nthe border to Saint Moritz.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we caught up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:06.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look sharp, JoJo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:12.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I'm just saving up my strength,\Nthat's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:16.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry up and get that Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:19.65,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then we need to plan for the\Nfight with Wamuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:21.64,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait until we cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.10,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:28.62,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:31.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go on, just pass us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:34.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,German soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:38.19,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing\Non the Swiss-Italian border?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:43.49,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking rather spry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:46.95,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My, how you've grown, Mr. Joestar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:49.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:53.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,G-Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:59.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!\NI don't know any German soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:01.61,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:03.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So many soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:05.93,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We found it, Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:09.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That crest! It's the package!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:11.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And we know what's inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:19.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Red Stone of Aja!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:22.49,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why do the Germans want it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:28.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We are taking the Stone as a specimen\Nfor our research.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:34.08,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For the past three weeks,\Nwe have been watching you in Venice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:38.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We started when we lost\Nour team in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:42.17,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We saw your training. We saw Esidisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:45.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And we knew you were chasing the Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:49.01,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our base is a lodge up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:50.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Follow us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:55.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We want to ask you about the Stone and Kars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:57.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let us work together, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:21:00.99,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We are not complete strangers, JoJo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:04.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you blabbing about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:07.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you know me, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:09.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So the Germans are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:10.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,C-Coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:12.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:16.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At least Kars doesn't have the Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:22.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, the German army\Nwas marching across Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:21.57,Type,Default,0000,0000,0000,,March 13, 1938: Annexation of Austria
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:22.94,Type,Default,0000,0000,0000,,March 15, 1939: Annexation \Nof Bohemia and Moravia
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:26.84,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They wanted to ensure their rule\Nwas permanent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:26.83,Type,Default,0000,0000,0000,,September 28, 1939: Division \Nof Poland with Soviet Union
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:34.30,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The power of the mask and Red Stone\Nwould solve their problem perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:36.71,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Germans needed the ultimate power
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:39.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nof immortality to conquer the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:43.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Five hours later - 10:00 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:57.42,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll read the heat inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:21:59.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The fireplace is lit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:03.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Four lights on the wall,\Ntwo on the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:04.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Two on the desk...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:06.34,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:10.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Four humans standing by the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.36,0:22:16.35,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From the right, their heights are\N178 cm, 174 cm, 181 cm, 178 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:20.61,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One human is by the fireplace.\NHe's 183 cm tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:23.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Five humans, all male.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:38.04,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:39.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's four.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.67,0:22:40.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And five.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:48.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Kars?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:49.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:54.85,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In just a few hours, you heard\Nabout your friend's defeat,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.40,0:22:58.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,then learned that we had obtained\Nthe Stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.56,0:23:00.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and have come for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:04.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And this brutal, calculated assault...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:08.49,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,None of my men made a sound\Nbefore they died.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:12.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there were five men\Nin this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:17.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, why can't I sense your body heat?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:19.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, rifle heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.33,0:23:21.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have to wait forever for food?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:24.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kars!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.67,0:23:28.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's mechanical!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:29.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:33.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...von Stroheim!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.65,0:25:08.65,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.19,0:25:10.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We should attack now!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.73,0:25:12.99,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That building is the address.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.99,0:25:14.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was mean of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.96,0:25:17.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is German science!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.33,0:25:19.08,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No machine can stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.66,0:25:22.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter 19: A Race Toward the Brink
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.13,0:25:24.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
